            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Navigation expertise empowers characters to rapidly assess and traverse unfamiliar or treacherous terrain, from cursed swamps to crumbling castle ruins. By reading signs like moss-covered stones, the flicker of distant torchlight, or the eerie howls of unseen creatures, they can chart a course through danger or disarray. This skill shines when time is short\u2014whether escaping a collapsing cavern or guiding allies past a dragon\u2019s lair\u2014relying on sharp instincts and spatial awareness.",
